metadata.name: poggu #1
metadata.description: hey everyone, i invested more than i could afford to lose and my bags have been very down for a long time... and so have i =( i think a lot of you that are here feel the same lately, i wanted to do something about feeling sad all the time. the wagmi is gone, so i made this collection for us. its poggu, poggu has good days, he has bad days poggu is our friend and poggu is there to love us. anyways i hope you like all these poggu i drew them myself and made the contract, i included a couple things from communities that have helped me and treat me like family. thank you for being you.
